<body>
    <% if (!role) { %>
        <%- include('home-navbar') %>
            <% } else { %>
                <%- include(role==='Admin' ? 'admin-navbar' : role==='Specialist' ? 'specialist-navbar'
                    : 'patient-navbar' ) %>
                    <% } %>

                        <div class="about-container">
                            <section class="about-section">
                                <h1>About CareConnect</h1>
                                <p>About CareConnect
                                    CareConnect is a comprehensive health platform dedicated to connecting patients with
                                    the right healthcare professionals. Our mission is to deliver top-notch medical
                                    services and support to improve the health and well-being of our clients.</p>
                            </section>

                            <section class="vision-section">
                                <h2>Our Vision</h2>
                                <p>TAt CareConnect, we envision a world where individuals can easily access the
                                    healthcare services they need, allowing them to lead healthier, happier lives. We
                                    strive to be a leader in the healthcare technology space, providing solutions that
                                    prioritize patient experience and health outcomes.</p>
                            </section>

                            <section class="vision-section">
                                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                                <p>Our mission is simple yet profound: to empower patients by giving them direct access
                                    to qualified healthcare professionals and personalized medical care. We understand
                                    that navigating the healthcare system can be overwhelming, and we're here to
                                    simplify that journey by connecting patients with the right providers, no matter
                                    their specific needs.</p>
                            </section>
